                            <comment id="15711726" author="mreutegg" created="Thu, 1 Dec 2016 11:33:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in trunk: &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1772172&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1772172&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Slightly changed the behaviour when a document with binaries is split. Now the split introduced with &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-2392&quot; title=&quot;[DocumentMK] Garbage Collect older revisions of binary properties in main document&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;OAK-2392&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;OAK-2392&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; only kicks in when the binary is larger than 4kB.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
